| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4948 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 589bcbfc-9f5e-5089-a64d-efe294d680a9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
